docs.summary: Status list of npm packages that have been requested.
description: Wix Code allows you to install some of the most popular npm packages in your
site. If you don't see a package you would like to use in the list of available
packages, you can request that it be added to the list.
To learn more about adding npm packages to your site or to learn how to request
a new package, see How to Manage External Code Libraries with the Package Manager.
